==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Preadamite
<hw>Pre*ad"am*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>pr⟦eacute⟧adamite</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An inhabitant of
the earth before Adam.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who holds that men existed before
Adam.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Preadamitic</ent>⟦br⟧
